Participant Consent
Interactive form for on-line consent

STUDENT RESEARCH PROJECT ETHICS REVIEW
Division of Psychiatry & Applied Psychology

Project Title: Nature of co-occurring worry in Autism
Researcher: Trishita Barua
Supervisor: Dr. Indu Dubey
Ethics Reference Number: DPAP - 2022 - 2883 - 3
Please select the following statements if you agree with them. Please feel free to withdraw at any point.
1. Have you read and understood the Participant Information?
2. Do you agree to take part in the online questionnaire and choose-a-movie task about the role of anxiety in autism?
3. Do you know how to contact the researcher if you have questions about this study?
4. Do you understand that you are free to withdraw from the study without giving a reason?
5. Do you understand that once you have taken part it may not be technically possible to withdraw your data?
6. Do you give permission for your data from this study to be shared with other researchers in the future provided that your anonymity is protected?
7. Do you understand that non-identifiable data from this study including quotations might be used in academic research reports or publications?
8. I confirm that I am 18 years old or over
If you would like a summary of the research findings please insert your email address in this text box
If you would like enter the prize draw please insert your email address in this text box
